{"tid":1095334,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"來緊14日波蘭烏克蘭旅行，求意見","createTime":"2019-04-07T03:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T16:32:39.000Z","uid":63190,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"099480949625f63df80681b1a14282c5b3f025e2","tid":1095334,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"我就咁plan<br />\nDay 1 華沙落機<br />\nDay 2 早上華沙出發去gdansk<br />\nDay 3 中午gdansk出發去wroclaw<br />\nDay 4 中午wroclaw出發去zakopane<br />\nDay 5 zakopane<br />\nDay 6 下午zakopane出發去krakow<br />\nDay 7-8 留krakow, 會去集中營，鹽礦<br />\nDay 9 krakow去烏克蘭lviv<br />\nDay 10 lviv<br />\nDay 11 lviv 去kamianets podilskyi<br />\nDay 12 kamianets podilskyi 去kiev<br />\nDay 13 kiev返去華沙<br />\nDay 14華沙返香港<br />\n<br />\n想問巴打，會不會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc031eae81cc2965e3a19f641a74da423e1eccc","tid":1095334,"uid":63190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"定係取消kamianets podilski, 因為去得呢度就join不到切爾諾貝爾tour"},{"pid":"df4b20d463f4fccf2d48b207b005ce179f481871","tid":1095334,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"14日返大陸叫雞"},{"pid":"366e3447ed652a98cf792e269a65a96a1c377f14","tid":1095334,"uid":71427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T04:39:14.000Z","msg":"去Wroclaw不如去Malborg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。其實波蘭個個old town差唔多樣"},{"pid":"faf0248fe155f8c718f3e588a9edfa3677429ceb","tid":1095334,"uid":31203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"幾錢budget?"},{"pid":"df991cef827fc2a3fbea7167c8670b964ee21223","tid":1095334,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"366e3447ed652a98cf792e269a65a96a1c377f14","tid":1095334,"uid":71427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T04:39: