kow去烏克蘭lviv<br />\nDay 10 lviv<br />\nDay 11 lviv 去kamianets podilskyi<br />\nDay 12 kamianets podilskyi 去kiev<br />\nDay 13 kiev返去華沙<br />\nDay 14華沙返香港<br />\n<br />\n想問巴打，會不會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"波蘭太多人答唔晒時間打lu<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭：<br />\nkrakow to lviv 如果搭巴士嘅話要有心理準備，大約8個鐘，搭完個日都無心情玩<br />\n<br />\nlviv 本身無咩野玩，純粹係一個relax嘅地方，但如果得1日又好似做唔到relax嘅效果。lviv 好多好嘅餐廳，d酒都幾唔錯，同埋記住攞tourist card<br />\n<br />\nkamianets podilskyi 未去過<br />\n<br />\n如果想去埋chernobyl, kyiv 起碼要玩三日，都幾多值得睇嘅教堂<br />\n<br />\n總結：都幾chur"},{"pid":"a00cd39373e4927cfaee0bcf4d256c9e48704c39","tid":1095334,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b591a7a3b3e87694c4925dab2c8189137bf69b1","tid":1095334,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"099480949625f63df80681b1a14282c5b3f025e2","tid":1095334,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"我就咁plan<br />\nDay 1 華沙落機<br />\nDay 2 早上華沙出發去gdansk<br />\nDay 3 中午gdansk出發去wroclaw<br />\nDay 4 中午wroclaw出發去zakopane<br />\nDay 5 zakopane<br />\nDay 6 下午zakopane出發去krakow<br />\nDay 7-8 留krakow, 會去集中營，鹽礦<br />\nDay 9 krakow去烏克蘭lviv<br />\nDay 10 lviv<br />\nDay 11 lviv 去kamianets podilskyi<br />\nDay 12 kamianets podilskyi 去kiev<br />\nDay 13 kiev返去華沙<br />\nDay 14華沙返香港<br />\n<br />\n想問巴打，會不會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"波蘭太多人答唔晒時間打lu<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭：<br />\nkrakow to lviv 如果搭巴士嘅話要有心理準備，大約8個鐘，搭完個日都無心情玩<br />\n<br />\nlviv 本身無咩野玩，純粹係一個relax嘅地方，但如果得1日又好似做唔到relax嘅效果。lviv 好多好嘅餐廳，d酒都幾唔錯，同埋記住攞tourist card<br />\n<br />\nkamianets podilskyi 未去過<br />\n<br />\n如果想去埋chernobyl, kyiv 起碼要玩三日，都幾多值得睇嘅教堂<br />\n<br />\n總結：都幾chur"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:42:41